phrases: All right, we are going to begin the match between Class 1 and Class 7.
I want to go home and sleep.
I-I want to go home and sleep!
Is it too obvious I like him if I cheer for him?
It would be too obvious I like Kanda if I look at her, right?
Looks like it is down to you guys and us.
Just so you know, no one with a girlfriend
Can you make the next match?
Do not you know the rules?
All right, let us clean this up.
Chiaki, next match is the final, right?
I will be rooting for you.
Keisuke, I want to play in boys' soccer, too.
I do not think you can.
All right, we are starting the final match.
Just do not handle the ball.
Why are you telling me, Yo-chan?
Come on, why have not I let go?
I do not stand a chance.
I-I was just trying to get the ball.
It would have been ours if you had not touched it!
I do not need your help, idiot!
The ball was not out of play.
Class 4 is going to lose at this rate.
Let us all cheer for them.
I bet Kana is not cheering for me.
Dammit, Kana, you are not even my girlfriend anymore.
You really think you scream that I am an idiot
without making me want to act like a boyfriend?
I told you, I am not letting some chick's boyfriend take me down!
I am in a sports club.
So, again, you better watch yourselves.
Opening Ceremony Long Homeroom Opening Ceremony Short Homeroom Cleanup
Suga-yan, is the soccer club busy during summer break?
We are planning to go to the beach.
I am shy about wearing a swimsuit and stuff.
So am I, but everyone is coming.
Come on, Kana, go make up with Chiaki.
Chiaki, you guys are going to the beach with us, right?
I do not know, I am thinking about it.
Are you sure it is okay if I come?
Would not it get awkward if I came?
He says it depends on his club.
So you two are coming for sure, right, Yo-chan?
It will be weird trying to meet Chiaki once summer break starts.
There is actually no club work that day.
But going to the beach will make me think about Takano again,
even though I know there is nothing between us.
She does not think anything of it, does she?
I would just be miserable, going when she does not think anything of me.
It does not even say he read it.
So are you going to the beach or not?
It will suck if Sugawara-kun does not come, huh?
I knew I did not have a chance to begin with.
I guess Chiaki does not want to patch things up anymore.
I guess I am going to be alone this summer.
Sorry, that was a weird thing to ask.
I am going to the bathroom!
It is true that I am always thinking about Sugawara-kun these days.
And if Sugawara-kun does not come to the beach...
You did not see my message?
I was waiting for you, so we could talk in person.
You are going to patch things up with me?
No, we have broken up already.
No, Yo-chan's in the bathroom right now.
Are not you going to the beach?
Honestly, I did not think you would break up with me, no matter what.
If we patched things up now, it would be like that never happened.
I do not think our relationship would last like that.
So let us break up properly.
Once that is done, I want to confess again.
Oh, I decided not to go.
Nah, I just do not really like that kind of thing.
I do not think it will be fun if you are not there.
I will reject you a hundred times.
I do not want to lose you anymore, Kana.
I will have to buy a swimsuit for the beach, then.
